Title: MATZUO - Weighted Snagging Treble Hooks 10/0  8/0 - AKRDY
Content: We're selling the legendary Matzuo® Weighted Treble hooks. Ok, so maybe not legendary but these have been hot sellers on the market over the last couple years. First, for their great durability and second for cost. They are excellent for Seward and Prince William Sound where snagging is permitted. A true Alaskan experience since there's not many other fisheries that allow snagging fish like Alaska. Great durability in the hook and plenty of weight to keep the hook down in the water where the salmon are. Snag for Kings, Silver, or Reds. Happy Fishing and Bring it on Alaska!
Short Description: Weighted Treble hooks ideal for Alaskan snagging. Go after King Salmon, Silver Salmon, or Red Salmon with these quality hooks.

Furthest Spray Distance at 35 feet
Hottest Bear Spray Formula Available at 2.0% CRC
Highest Amount of Spray Volume

Unlike other brands that spray a slower forming narrow fog of bear pepper spray, UDAP Pepper Power® Bear Spray deploys a high volume powerful blast of highly concentrated pepper spray in a dense fog – covering a broader area in a much shorter period of time.

Title: Tuffo - Muddy Buddy Rainsuits Red, Yellow, Blue, Pink, Camo - AKRDY
Content:
Tuffo Muddy Buddy Waterproof Coveralls for year-round play. Great for keeping underclothes clean and dry no matter the activity. Use Muddy Buddy suits indoors for arts and crafts or outdoors for mud, rain, at the beach, or helping with chores. These suits come in standard sizes from 12 months to 5T. Lightweight and easy fits over clothes for ease of changing clothes. Muddy Buddy suit comes with a carrying case for easy storage. FEATURES:
  • Dual Front Zippers for quick, on-the-go changes
  • Generous fit allows for layering of clothing and easy movement
  • Elasticized hood with brim to shed water
  • Seams are sealed to ensure waterproofness
  • Elasticized wrist and ankle cuffs fit over mitts and boots
  • Machine wash cold, hang to dry
  • Weight: 0.45 lbs / 200 grams
Short Description: Tuffo Muddy Buddy Waterproof Coverall Suits

Title: Columbia River Tackle - Weighted Snagging Treble Hooks, Classic 10/0  8/0  6/0  - AKRDY
Content:
These snagging hooks resemble the standard setup with the weight attached to the main shaft of the hook. These come in 10/0, 8/0, and 6/0 weighted snagging hooks. Made in Palmer, AK by Columbia River Tackle.

***FREE SHIPPING TO JBER***
Short Description: These Columbia River Tackle weighted treble hooks are great for snagging salmon at Seward, Prince William Sound, and anywhere else snagging is legal in Alaska. The 10/0 are bigger than the 6/0. Get pink salmon, silver salmon, or King Salmon with these hooks.

Title: MATZUO - Weighted Snagging Treble Hooks 10/0  8/0 - AKRDY
Content: We're selling the legendary Matzuo® Weighted Treble hooks. Ok, so maybe not legendary but these have been hot sellers on the market over the last couple years. First, for their great durability and second for cost. They are excellent for Seward and Prince William Sound where snagging is permitted. A true Alaskan experience since there's not many other fisheries that allow snagging fish like Alaska. Great durability in the hook and plenty of weight to keep the hook down in the water where the salmon are. Snag for Kings, Silver, or Reds. Happy Fishing and Bring it on Alaska!
Short Description: Weighted Treble hooks ideal for Alaskan snagging. Go after King Salmon, Silver Salmon, or Red Salmon with these quality hooks.

This is a convenient setup for fishing for both Kings and Silvers. Used for drifting roe. This kit comes with everything you need from the main line down.
  • Bead
  • Slip Knot
  • Bobber
  • 20lb leader line (Coho) or 30lb leader line (Chinook)
  • 1/2 oz weight (Coho) or 3/8oz weight (Chinook)
  • 3/0 hook (Coho) or 5/0 hook (Chinook)
